    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*This is only a demo and does not represent the full game*</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/7f52b0ba338bb85c4d501dd2dd525c96.avif?t=1742807980\" width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Unsolved is a detective story-driven game where you step into the shoes of an investigator, gathering clues, interrogating suspects, and connecting evidence to solve complex murder cases. Your goal is to uncover the identity of a serial killer who has left a trail of destruction in your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/f35ad685bda46b023d51ef66b7d2ad74.avif?t=1742807980\" width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/1db4905546fbcc9148555df6b33b6d41.poster.avif?t=1742807980\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/1db4905546fbcc9148555df6b33b6d41.webm?t=1742807980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/1db4905546fbcc9148555df6b33b6d41.mp4?t=1742807980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Start by gathering clues, whether it’s a weapon, a witness, or a simple note.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/f22b066643909ae4cef395b17447bdfe.avif?t=1742807980\" width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/71c3f5df0adf6f9e224acdef3fd627f6.poster.avif?t=1742807980\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/71c3f5df0adf6f9e224acdef3fd627f6.webm?t=1742807980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171890/extras/71c3f5df0adf6f9e224acdef3fd627f6.mp4?t=1742807980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect the clues you've gathered using a unique mechanic. </p>",
